Maintainer: Farhan Tahir <farhan.003@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/ftahirops/xtop
Description: Incident-first root-cause analysis console for Linux
 v0.42.1: xtop agent init now enables ResourceGuard by default — fresh
 agents get XTOP_GUARD=1 in /etc/xtop/fleet.env automatically. Opt out
 with --no-guard. Running xtop as a systemd-managed service is the
 recommended deployment; see `xtop setup` or `xtop agent init --help`.
